.field
  = f.label :name
  = f.text_field :name
  .explanation
    Should be at least four characters long, memorable, and probably hilarious.
.field
  = f.label :password
  = f.password_field :password
.field
  = f.label :password_confirmation
  = f.password_field :password_confirmation
  .explanation
    Your teammates will need this to join your team.
    Should be strong but not obnoxiously so.
.field.checkbox
  = f.label :fun, "We're just playing for the fun of it"
  = f.check_box :fun
  .explanation
    If you've already qualified or can't come to Las Vegas in August,
    this'll save us some time contacting you. If you're not sure,
    leave this unchecked.
.field
  = f.label :logo
  = f.file_field :logo
  .explanation
    A logo so you can identify your team easily. Must be GIF, JPEG, or PNG.
    Must be 128kb or less. Square is cool, 4:3 aspect ratio also works.
